
    sequenceDiagram
        participant M as Main
        participant U as User
        participant S as Session
        participant St as Statistics
        M->>U: create user
        M->>S: create session
        S->>U: load progress
        S->>S: generate text
        S->>S: get input
        S->>S: end session
        S->>U: save progress
        M->>St: create statistics
        St->>St: collect data
        St->>St: display data
    